title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: The JarExporter functionality is causing the application to go out of sync.
OB: The exported jar file includes itself, leading to synchronization issues.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself.
SR:
To reproduce this bug:
1. Enable the JarExporter functionality.
2. Export a jar file.
3. Check if the exported jar file includes itself.
